Traffic Selectors for Flow Bindings
2011", shape=ellipse, URL="RFC6088.html", target="_top", tooltip="This document defines binary formats for IPv4 and IPv6 traffic selectors to be used in conjunction with flow bindings for Mobile IPv6. [STANDARDS-TRACK]"];
